00:01:25.080 --> 00:01:26.260
Staying hydrated,

00:01:26.260 --> 00:01:27.480
eating a healthy diet,

00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:29.440
especially foods rich in calcium,

00:01:29.440 --> 00:01:31.140
potassium and magnesium,

00:01:31.140 --> 00:01:32.980
and stretching regularly

00:01:32.980 --> 00:01:35.940
are the best ways to prevent muscle cramps.
